{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_yang_guang","speaker_name":"阳光","listener":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","text":"我以为你想不到我会带他走这条路的，想不到你还是找来了。","tone":"无奈","chapter":35,"line_start":10,"line_end":10},{"speaker":"char_yang_guang","speaker_name":"阳光","listener":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","text":"难怪每个人都说，如果班察巴那要追踪一个人，就好像猎犬要追一只鸡，从来没有一次追不到的。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":35,"line_start":12,"line_end":12},{"speaker":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","speaker_name":"班察巴那","listener":null,"text":"你们知不知道是谁对她下的毒手？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":16,"line_end":18},{"speaker":"char_yang_guang","speaker_name":"阳光","listener":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","text":"你知道？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":20,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_yang_guang","speaker_name":"阳光","listener":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","text":"是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":20,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","speaker_name":"班察巴那","listener":"char_yang_guang","text":"是金手。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":22,"line_end":22},{"speaker":"char_yang_guang","speaker_name":"阳光","listener":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","text":"金手？金手是什么人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":24,"line_end":24},{"speaker":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","speaker_name":"班察巴那","listener":"char_yang_guang","text":"金手不是一个人，是一个组织，是吕三用黄金收买的组织。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":26,"line_end":26},{"speaker":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","speaker_name":"班察巴那","listener":"char_yang_guang","text":"金手就是他们用的代号。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":28,"line_end":28},{"speaker":"char_yang_guang","speaker_name":"阳光","listener":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","text":"以前我们为什么没听见过？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":30,"line_end":30},{"speaker":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","speaker_name":"班察巴那","listener":"char_yang_guang","text":"这我也是最近才知道的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":32,"line_end":32},{"speaker":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","speaker_name":"班察巴那","listener":"char_yang_guang","text":"铁翼、卫天鹏、柳分分，都是这组织中的人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":32,"line_end":34},{"speaker":"char_yang_guang","speaker_name":"阳光","listener":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","text":"柳分分既然也是这组织中的人，他们为什么要这样对付她？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":36,"line_end":36},{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":null,"text":"因为她曾经出卖过他们。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":40,"line_end":40},{"speaker":"char_yang_guang","speaker_name":"阳光","listener":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","text":"他们故意把柳分分吊在这里，是不是故意向我们示威？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":52,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_yang_guang","speaker_name":"阳光","listener":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","text":"一定是的，所以你应该赶快去找他们，给他们一点颜色看。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":56,"line_end":58},{"speaker":"char_yang_guang","speaker_name":"阳光","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"我们也应该走了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":62,"line_end":62},{"speaker":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","speaker_name":"班察巴那","listener":"char_yang_guang","text":"你走，他留下。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":64,"line_end":64},{"speaker":"char_yang_guang","speaker_name":"阳光","listener":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","text":"你要他留下来干什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":66,"line_end":66},{"speaker":"char_yang_guang","speaker_name":"阳光","listener":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","text":"是不是要他陪你喝酒？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":66,"line_end":68},{"speaker":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","speaker_name":"班察巴那","listener":"char_yang_guang","text":"不是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":70,"line_end":70},{"speaker":"char_yang_guang","speaker_name":"阳光","listener":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","text":"我也知道你当然不是要他陪你喝酒，你要杀人时从不喝酒。","tone":"无奈","chapter":35,"line_start":74,"line_end":76},{"speaker":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","speaker_name":"班察巴那","listener":"char_yang_guang","text":"你明明知道，为什么还要问？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":80,"line_end":80},{"speaker":"char_yang_guang","speaker_name":"阳光","listener":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","text":"因为我希望你只不过是要他陪你喝杯酒而已。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":82,"line_end":82},{"speaker":"char_yang_guang","speaker_name":"阳光","listener":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","text":"因为你是绝对杀不了他的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":84,"line_end":84},{"speaker":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","speaker_name":"班察巴那","listener":"char_yang_guang","text":"我明白你的意思。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":35,"line_start":88,"line_end":88},{"speaker":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","speaker_name":"班察巴那","listener":"char_yang_guang","text":"你们两个人不妨一起出手，只要能杀了我，你可以带他走。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":35,"line_start":88,"line_end":90},{"speaker":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","speaker_name":"班察巴那","listener":"char_yang_guang","text":"只有杀了我，你才能带他走。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":92,"line_end":92},{"speaker":"char_yang_guang","speaker_name":"阳光","listener":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","text":"你错了，你根本不明白我的意思，我根本不想杀你，但是你也绝不能杀他，否则……","tone":"无奈","chapter":35,"line_start":96,"line_end":96},{"speaker":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","speaker_name":"班察巴那","listener":"char_yang_guang","text":"否则怎么样？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":98,"line_end":98},{"speaker":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","speaker_name":"班察巴那","listener":"char_yang_guang","text":"他要走时，谁也拦不住他，我要杀人时，也同样没有人能拦得住我。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":100,"line_end":100}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[{"id":"faction_jin_shou","name":"金手","type":"帮派","location":"未知","sub_divisions":[],"one_line":"吕三用黄金收买的组织，代号金手","source_refs":[{"chapter":35,"line_start":26,"line_end":26,"text":"金手不是一个人，是一个组织，是吕三用黄金收买的组织。"}]}],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":200,"line_end":308,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_qi_lv_de_pang_zi","speaker_name":"骑驴的胖子","listener":"char_kuan_jian_feng_yao_de_da_han","text":"你说的就是这地方？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":210,"line_end":212},{"speaker":"char_kuan_jian_feng_yao_de_da_han","speaker_name":"宽肩蜂腰的大汉","listener":"char_qi_lv_de_pang_zi","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":214,"line_end":214},{"speaker":"char_qi_lv_de_pang_zi","speaker_name":"骑驴的胖子","listener":"char_kuan_jian_feng_yao_de_da_han","text":"我记得你好像说这地方是个绿洲。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":216,"line_end":216},{"speaker":"char_kuan_jian_feng_yao_de_da_han","speaker_name":"宽肩蜂腰的大汉","listener":"char_qi_lv_de_pang_zi","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":218,"line_end":218},{"speaker":"char_qi_lv_de_pang_zi","speaker_name":"骑驴的胖子","listener":"char_kuan_jian_feng_yao_de_da_han","text":"绿洲是不是都有水的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":220,"line_end":220},{"speaker":"char_kuan_jian_feng_yao_de_da_han","speaker_name":"宽肩蜂腰的大汉","listener":"char_qi_lv_de_pang_zi","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":222,"line_end":222},{"speaker":"char_qi_lv_de_pang_zi","speaker_name":"骑驴的胖子","listener":"char_kuan_jian_feng_yao_de_da_han","text":"水在哪里？","tone":"无奈","chapter":35,"line_start":224,"line_end":224},{"speaker":"char_qi_lv_de_pang_zi","speaker_name":"骑驴的胖子","listener":"char_kuan_jian_feng_yao_de_da_han","text":"我怎么连一滴水都看不见？","tone":"无奈","chapter":35,"line_start":224,"line_end":224},{"speaker":"char_qi_lv_de_pang_zi","speaker_name":"骑驴的胖子","listener":"char_kuan_jian_feng_yao_de_da_han","text":"想不到，真是想不到。","tone":"无奈","chapter":35,"line_start":232,"line_end":232},{"speaker":"char_qi_lv_de_pang_zi","speaker_name":"骑驴的胖子","listener":"char_kuan_jian_feng_yao_de_da_han","text":"最近你身体好不好？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":234,"line_end":234},{"speaker":"char_kuan_jian_feng_yao_de_da_han","speaker_name":"宽肩蜂腰的大汉","listener":"char_qi_lv_de_pang_zi","text":"还好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":236,"line_end":236},{"speaker":"char_qi_lv_de_pang_zi","speaker_name":"骑驴的胖子","listener":"char_kuan_jian_feng_yao_de_da_han","text":"有没有生过什么病？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":238,"line_end":238},{"speaker":"char_kuan_jian_feng_yao_de_da_han","speaker_name":"宽肩蜂腰的大汉","listener":"char_qi_lv_de_pang_zi","text":"没有。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":240,"line_end":240},{"speaker":"char_qi_lv_de_pang_zi","speaker_name":"骑驴的胖子","listener":"char_kuan_jian_feng_yao_de_da_han","text":"那么我猜你一定也想不到自己会死的。","tone":"无奈","chapter":35,"line_start":242,"line_end":242},{"speaker":"char_qi_lv_de_pang_zi","speaker_name":"骑驴的胖子","listener":"char_kuan_jian_feng_yao_de_da_han","text":"你觉得很好笑？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":248,"line_end":248},{"speaker":"char_kuan_jian_feng_yao_de_da_han","speaker_name":"宽肩蜂腰的大汉","listener":"char_qi_lv_de_pang_zi","text":"我……我……我……","tone":"痛苦","chapter":35,"line_start":250,"line_end":250}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_qi_lv_de_pang_zi","name":"骑驴的胖子","alias":[],"identity":"神秘人物","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登峰造极","one_line":"骑驴的高大肥胖男子，看似老实忠厚却带有杀机","personality":{"traits":["深不可测","看似忠厚","实则残忍","喜怒无常","神秘莫测"],"speech_style":"慢吞吞","temperament":"平静"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[35],"source_refs":[{"chapter":35,"line_start":200,"line_end":200,"text":"这个人高大肥胖，骑的却偏偏是匹又瘦又小的驴子。"}]},{"id":"char_kuan_jian_feng_yao_de_da_han","name":"宽肩蜂腰的大汉","alias":[],"identity":"手下","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"宽肩蜂腰的大汉，对骑驴胖子极为畏惧","personality":{"traits":["恐惧","顺从","胆小","忠诚","痛苦"],"speech_style":"简短","temperament":"恐惧"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[35],"source_refs":[{"chapter":35,"line_start":210,"line_end":210,"text":"才向一条宽肩蜂腰的大汉招了招手"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
